WEBVTT

01:43.080 --> 01:45.000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

01:50.560 --> 01:52.000
Go and get changed first.

01:53.440 --> 01:54.280
It will be fine.

03:26.200 --> 03:27.360
Sang Yan,

03:27.440 --> 03:28.360
how is your sister?

03:28.440 --> 03:29.600
She's okay.

03:29.680 --> 03:31.680
Let's talk to her over dinner.

03:31.760 --> 03:32.800
We don't need to.

03:32.880 --> 03:34.000
She knows her mistake.

03:34.080 --> 03:35.200
She cried the whole way.

03:35.280 --> 03:36.160
I already scolded her.

03:36.800 --> 03:37.840
I think that's enough.

03:40.440 --> 03:41.760
Do you think she's…

03:43.040 --> 03:45.080
Duan Jiaxu said that guy
didn't make any promises.

03:45.160 --> 03:46.360
It was her wishful thinking.

03:47.640 --> 03:49.720
With her proud personality,

03:49.800 --> 03:51.360
if she said it's over, it's really over.

03:53.320 --> 03:54.560
She would see it through.

03:54.640 --> 03:55.680
Think about it.

03:55.760 --> 03:57.720
Whenever she said
she would stop binging anime,

03:57.800 --> 03:58.680
she would stop.

03:58.760 --> 04:00.800
Has she ever kept a plushie
that she dislikes?

04:01.560 --> 04:02.600
You're right about that.

04:03.080 --> 04:04.400
It's her teenage rebellion phase.

04:04.480 --> 04:06.320
It's normal to rebel once.

04:06.880 --> 04:08.960
How about not criticizing her then?

04:09.040 --> 04:10.360
Okay.

04:10.440 --> 04:12.600
We'll pretend nothing happened
during dinner.

04:13.480 --> 04:15.800
As if she came home from school as usual.

04:17.880 --> 04:20.880
We need to hold onto her ID card

04:20.959 --> 04:23.280
and pay attention to what she does online.

04:24.160 --> 04:25.360
We also need to take her phone.

04:25.440 --> 04:27.200
Yes, we have to confiscate her phone.

04:30.360 --> 04:32.680
Take this cold medicine upstairs
to her later.

04:33.200 --> 04:34.480
She wore a short skirt.

04:34.560 --> 04:35.640
Don't let her catch a cold.

04:35.720 --> 04:36.720
Okay.

05:29.480 --> 05:32.160
YIHE UNIVERSITY

05:34.200 --> 05:36.280
YIHE UNIVERSITY

05:43.880 --> 05:48.400
NANWU, YIHE, MAP TO MY DREAM

06:21.720 --> 06:25.360
PURE MILK

07:23.120 --> 07:24.000
Jiaxu.

07:25.680 --> 07:27.800
I finally found my dream.

07:30.320 --> 07:31.960
My dream is to get into Yihe University.

07:32.040 --> 07:36.960
MY DREAM, YIHE UNIVERSITY

07:40.120 --> 07:46.760
YIHE UNIVERSITY

07:46.840 --> 07:53.440
YIHE UNIVERSITY

07:53.520 --> 07:58.120
DUAN JIAXU

07:58.200 --> 08:03.280
DUAN JIAXU

08:03.360 --> 08:08.520
DUAN JIAXU

08:13.200 --> 08:19.280
DUAN JIAXU

08:19.360 --> 08:25.440
DUAN JIAXU

09:00.880 --> 09:02.000
Jiaxu.

09:04.400 --> 09:05.400
Goodbye.

09:09.720 --> 09:11.880
NOVEMBER 5TH, SATURDAY

09:11.960 --> 09:16.880
GOODBYE, JIAXU

09:18.320 --> 09:23.680
TWO YEARS LATER

09:39.160 --> 09:40.680
So I've fulfilled my dream

09:41.320 --> 09:43.040
and been admitted into Yihe University.

09:43.680 --> 09:47.000
I've started a new life here.

09:48.320 --> 09:49.560
I've attended military training

09:50.080 --> 09:51.400
and I'm attending my lectures.

09:52.480 --> 09:54.000
I've also made new friends

09:54.600 --> 09:56.200
and met my lovely roommates.

09:57.240 --> 09:58.280
Hello, everyone.

09:58.360 --> 10:00.560
Welcome to my vlog.

10:00.640 --> 10:02.200
Today, I want to show you

10:02.280 --> 10:04.920
the most beautiful view at my university.

10:05.000 --> 10:05.840
So what could it be?

10:07.280 --> 10:08.240
Hello, sorry about that.

10:08.320 --> 10:09.280
Hi.

10:10.400 --> 10:11.560
He's so handsome!

10:12.600 --> 10:13.760
I'm so proud!

10:13.840 --> 10:16.200
To the side is our lecture building.

10:16.280 --> 10:17.360
Let me show you around.

10:18.920 --> 10:21.160
Let's see who that cool girl is!

10:23.480 --> 10:25.360
It's Yu Xin, the coolest girl on campus!

10:25.440 --> 10:26.920
For her first cameo in my vlog,

10:27.000 --> 10:29.560
- this is embarrassing!
- You got in my way. Delete it.

10:35.440 --> 10:36.560
Sorry about that!

10:40.440 --> 10:41.520
I'll go and check on her.

10:43.880 --> 10:45.800
Miss, are you okay?

10:45.880 --> 10:46.880
I'm fine.

10:46.960 --> 10:48.240
Let me help you.

10:49.720 --> 10:50.560
Thank you.

10:51.080 --> 10:52.680
Why are you carrying so many books alone?

10:53.640 --> 10:54.720
My classmates are all busy.

10:54.800 --> 10:56.240
I'm fetching books for my professor.

10:56.320 --> 10:58.040
Where are you headed? I'll carry them.

10:58.120 --> 10:59.880
The Digital Media Department up ahead.

10:59.960 --> 11:01.320
Let's go then.

11:01.400 --> 11:02.360
Thank you.

11:15.800 --> 11:16.680
Sangsang!

11:17.440 --> 11:18.440
Where's Wangwang?

11:21.200 --> 11:22.480
Wangwang?

11:22.560 --> 11:24.920
Let me show you my best friend.

11:26.000 --> 11:28.120
- She's over there.
- Why are you talking like that?

11:28.680 --> 11:30.840
- Hi.
- Who is this?

11:32.000 --> 11:33.080
He's just--

11:33.160 --> 11:35.760
Hi, I'm Jiang Ming
in the long-distance running team.

11:35.840 --> 11:37.200
I'm helping her carry these books.

11:37.280 --> 11:38.800
So you're in the Sports Department.

11:38.880 --> 11:40.080
We're in Digital Media.

11:40.160 --> 11:41.360
We're all roommates.

11:41.440 --> 11:42.560
Hello.

11:43.320 --> 11:44.200
Hello.

11:44.280 --> 11:46.520
Since we've met,
let's add each other on WeChat.

11:46.600 --> 11:48.000
It's my birthday tomorrow.

11:48.080 --> 11:50.120
Invite your friends to come to my party.

11:50.600 --> 11:51.760
Sure, no problem.

11:51.840 --> 11:52.880
Let me scan your QR code.

11:52.960 --> 11:54.560
Sure, here you go.

11:54.640 --> 11:55.560
Come on, scan his code.

11:55.640 --> 11:57.520
She can forward it to us later.

11:58.280 --> 11:59.440
Okay, I'll do that.

11:59.520 --> 12:00.960
Then you can send me

12:01.040 --> 12:02.760
the time and location later.

12:02.840 --> 12:03.800
No problem.

12:05.680 --> 12:07.200
I'll get that. Thank you for your help.

12:07.280 --> 12:08.160
But…

12:08.240 --> 12:09.120
It's okay.

12:09.200 --> 12:10.480
Why don't you walk her there?

12:10.560 --> 12:11.760
Go with her.

12:13.000 --> 12:14.280
Okay, then…

12:15.640 --> 12:17.120
It's that building.

12:17.200 --> 12:19.280
Okay. Then we'll get going.

12:20.480 --> 12:21.520
- Bye.
- Yes, go ahead.

12:21.600 --> 12:22.480
Bye.

12:22.560 --> 12:24.840
- Come tomorrow. Bring your friends.
- We'll wait to eat with you.

12:25.440 --> 12:27.080
- Cut it out, will you?
- What?

12:27.560 --> 12:29.080
What are we having for lunch?

12:29.160 --> 12:30.120
Anything will do.

12:33.000 --> 12:34.360
Can you keep up with us?

12:35.000 --> 12:35.920
No.

12:36.440 --> 12:37.360
Yes, you can.

12:42.600 --> 12:43.800
This place is pretty spacious.

12:43.880 --> 12:45.520
- Yes.
- I think my lipstick is too bright.

12:45.600 --> 12:46.880
- Let me wipe some off.
- Don't.

12:47.400 --> 12:48.280
I think it's pretty.

12:48.360 --> 12:50.280
I thought you weren't
wearing any lipstick.

12:50.360 --> 12:52.520
- Really?
- It's this year's latest trendy color.

12:52.600 --> 12:53.720
It looks good on everyone

12:53.800 --> 12:55.000
Just look at her complexion.

12:55.080 --> 12:56.640
It still can't be compared to mine.

12:56.720 --> 12:57.680
Hey, Ning Wei.

12:58.440 --> 12:59.400
Hi, Jiang Ming.

13:00.080 --> 13:01.280
- Hello.
- Hello.

13:01.920 --> 13:03.600
This is my teammate, Chen Qiang.

13:03.680 --> 13:04.520
Hi.

13:04.600 --> 13:05.720
- Hi.
- These are my classmates.

13:05.800 --> 13:07.400
They're in the Sports Department.

13:07.480 --> 13:08.320
- Hello.
- Hi.

13:08.400 --> 13:10.320
These are my friends from a school club.

13:10.400 --> 13:11.400
- Hello.
- Hello.

13:11.480 --> 13:12.640
There are so many people here.

13:12.720 --> 13:14.480
This is the birthday girl, Ning Wei.

13:14.560 --> 13:15.680
These are her roommates.

13:15.760 --> 13:17.360
- Happy birthday!
- Happy birthday!

13:17.440 --> 13:18.680
Thank you so much.

13:18.760 --> 13:20.440
Since everyone is here, let's head inside.

13:20.520 --> 13:21.920
- Okay, let's go.
- Come on.

13:22.000 --> 13:23.200
Let's go inside.

13:23.280 --> 13:24.160
Come on.

13:26.240 --> 13:28.360
Sangsang, today is my first birthday party

13:28.440 --> 13:29.600
at university.

13:30.080 --> 13:31.920
- The first one?
- How do you want to celebrate?

13:32.000 --> 13:32.920
I want

13:33.880 --> 13:35.520
to eat well, have fun,

13:35.600 --> 13:36.920
- and then party.
- Control yourself.

14:09.160 --> 14:11.360
CHAPTER EIGHT, REENCOUNTER

14:11.440 --> 14:13.280
SAYING GOODBYE BEFORE MEETING AGAIN

14:14.560 --> 14:18.720
Restless and fidgeting privileged guests

14:18.800 --> 14:20.640
- Presumptuous and conceited…
- Jiaxu, come.

14:20.720 --> 14:21.960
- Come here.
- Xiaoduan, sit here.

14:22.600 --> 14:23.600
Why are you so late?

14:24.480 --> 14:26.160
- I went to the restroom.
- Sit down.

14:26.240 --> 14:27.120
Xiaoduan.

14:27.680 --> 14:28.800
Let me do the introduction.

14:28.880 --> 14:30.920
She's my best friend, Xiaoxu.

14:31.000 --> 14:33.040
She works in HR at a foreign company.

14:33.120 --> 14:34.520
She was having dinner nearby,

14:34.600 --> 14:36.360
so I asked her to join us.

14:36.960 --> 14:38.880
This is Duan Jiaxu,

14:38.960 --> 14:40.320
our company's chief programmer.

14:40.400 --> 14:41.440
He's young and promising.

14:41.520 --> 14:42.800
Isn't he handsome?

14:42.880 --> 14:43.840
He is indeed handsome.

14:43.920 --> 14:44.960
It's nice to meet you.

14:46.200 --> 14:47.280
Hello.

14:48.600 --> 14:49.520
Hello.

14:52.720 --> 14:54.400
Stop being awkward. Come.

14:54.880 --> 14:56.960
Let's have a drink and become friends.

14:57.040 --> 14:58.440
I know you don't drink.

14:59.440 --> 15:01.800
We know you don't drink. Here.

15:01.880 --> 15:02.840
Thank you, buddy.

15:02.920 --> 15:04.440
Let's all have a drink together.

15:04.520 --> 15:05.880
- Cheers.
- Cheers to Xiaoxu.

15:05.960 --> 15:07.440
- Here.
- Cheers.

15:07.520 --> 15:08.680
- Here, cheers.
- Cheers.

15:10.480 --> 15:11.720
Dear, what's the title

15:11.800 --> 15:13.880
of the song that we just dueted?

15:13.960 --> 15:16.240
- It's called…
- "Like Falling Into a Sea of Love".

15:16.320 --> 15:17.760
- Yes, that's it.
- Don't stand around.

15:17.840 --> 15:19.360
- Pick this song.
- Skip the rest.

15:19.440 --> 15:22.160
Xiaoduan, our offices are close together.

15:22.240 --> 15:24.000
You two can meet up for coffee sometime.

15:24.080 --> 15:26.040
- Sure.
- I haven't heard you sing in a while.

15:26.120 --> 15:27.280
Sing one for me.

15:27.360 --> 15:28.320
The song is playing.

15:29.720 --> 15:30.840
Xiaoxu, join in.

15:33.600 --> 15:36.240
I want to live in your heart

15:54.680 --> 15:57.480
- They are also happy fruit people
- They are also happy fruit people

16:00.440 --> 16:05.080
- They are also happy fruit people
- They are also happy fruit people

16:06.320 --> 16:07.640
What do you usually like to do?

16:08.960 --> 16:10.480
What do you usually enjoy doing?

16:12.240 --> 16:13.080
Read comics.

16:14.000 --> 16:15.280
Do you have any recommendations?

16:16.600 --> 16:18.560
It depends on your preferences.

16:20.560 --> 16:22.560
Do you like outdoor activities?

16:22.640 --> 16:23.760
For example, hiking.

16:23.840 --> 16:24.920
No.

16:25.000 --> 16:26.200
What about amusement parks?

16:27.080 --> 16:28.000
No.

16:28.480 --> 16:29.880
- Next time, do you want to--
- Hey!

16:29.960 --> 16:31.200
It's my birthday.

16:31.280 --> 16:33.000
Why are the three of you flirting here?

16:33.080 --> 16:34.760
Hurry and sing and dance for me!

16:34.840 --> 16:36.560
Go quickly. Hurry up.

16:37.960 --> 16:40.160
Weiwei, happy birthday!

16:40.240 --> 16:41.680
Happy birthday!

16:44.840 --> 16:46.160
I'm going outside for some air.

16:46.240 --> 16:47.240
I'll be right back.

16:47.320 --> 16:48.160
Okay.

16:49.160 --> 16:54.040
- Treat it as a friend passing by
- Treat it as a friend passing by

17:08.000 --> 17:08.920
Sang Zhi?

17:32.720 --> 17:33.880
Did you start smoking?

17:35.000 --> 17:37.080
I don't smoke. That's not mine.

17:38.040 --> 17:39.080
I clearly saw it fall out

17:39.160 --> 17:40.440
from your pocket.

17:41.360 --> 17:42.720
You've picked up bad habits.

17:42.800 --> 17:43.720
I'm confiscating it.

17:45.640 --> 17:46.480
No.

17:47.160 --> 17:49.080
I told you it belongs to my friend.

17:49.800 --> 17:51.600
They may have misplaced it.

17:51.680 --> 17:53.800
- If you don't give it back--
- You've even been drinking.

17:59.600 --> 18:00.560
Just a little.

18:05.240 --> 18:06.520
I'll put the rest aside.

18:06.600 --> 18:08.640
It has been a while.
You didn't even greet me.

18:18.760 --> 18:19.720
Jiaxu.

18:21.920 --> 18:23.120
Did you come here to have fun?

18:23.840 --> 18:25.360
It's my roommate's birthday.

18:25.440 --> 18:27.320
When did your military training end?

18:27.400 --> 18:29.000
In the middle of last month.

18:29.080 --> 18:31.120
You didn't visit me
during the Golden Week holiday.

18:31.200 --> 18:32.160
I had classes.

18:33.760 --> 18:35.080
Classes during the holiday?

18:35.160 --> 18:36.240
My mistake.

18:37.600 --> 18:38.440
My part-time job.

18:39.800 --> 18:40.800
I see. A part-time job.

18:41.720 --> 18:42.880
Yes.

18:42.960 --> 18:44.280
I used to work part-time too.

18:44.960 --> 18:46.520
Other than working part-time,

18:46.600 --> 18:48.840
I had to meet your teacher,

18:48.920 --> 18:51.000
do your homework, and take you to school.

18:54.960 --> 18:56.120
Ungrateful thing.

18:58.360 --> 18:59.840
This kiddo has no conscience at all.

19:00.880 --> 19:01.720
Well, it's fine.

19:03.160 --> 19:04.040
Jiaxu.

19:04.120 --> 19:06.000
You were already a senior back then.

19:06.520 --> 19:07.600
I'm only a freshman.

19:08.080 --> 19:10.400
I might be a little busier than you were.

19:11.240 --> 19:12.720
Are you calling me old now?

19:14.000 --> 19:15.040
Sang Zhi.

19:15.120 --> 19:16.760
Take a moment and reflect.

19:16.840 --> 19:18.440
What exactly did I do wrong to you?

19:18.520 --> 19:19.800
I never said that.

19:22.160 --> 19:23.040
Also…

19:27.000 --> 19:28.520
I'm a grown-up now.

19:28.600 --> 19:31.080
If you keep calling me a kiddo,

19:31.160 --> 19:32.280
don't you think

19:32.360 --> 19:34.640
it's a little awkward?

19:34.720 --> 19:36.200
How old can you be?

19:36.280 --> 19:38.000
You're still a kid.

19:44.800 --> 19:45.680
Yes.

19:46.600 --> 19:48.000
I'm still a kid.

19:49.400 --> 19:50.480
Two years…

19:51.720 --> 19:52.920
After two years,

19:53.000 --> 19:54.640
you've indeed grown older

19:55.800 --> 19:56.760
and weathered.

20:00.560 --> 20:03.120
Sang Zhi, check your phone and see

20:03.200 --> 20:04.880
how many messages I've sent you.

20:04.960 --> 20:07.200
You didn't reply even once. Why?

20:07.280 --> 20:10.000
It's like I said. I had classes.

20:10.080 --> 20:11.640
Did you need to isolate yourself?

20:11.720 --> 20:12.840
Of course I had to.

20:12.920 --> 20:14.040
If I didn't,

20:14.120 --> 20:16.120
how else could I get into Yihe University?

20:22.560 --> 20:23.400
Fine.

20:25.600 --> 20:27.120
It's past nine and you're still out.

20:27.200 --> 20:28.240
I'm leaving soon.

20:28.320 --> 20:30.200
- Get your things. I'll see you back.
- It's okay.

20:30.280 --> 20:32.200
I can go back with my friends.

20:34.360 --> 20:35.400
That works too.

20:42.080 --> 20:42.960
Sang Zhi.

20:46.400 --> 20:47.640
It has been so long.

20:47.720 --> 20:49.160
You've learned how to put on makeup.

20:49.240 --> 20:50.800
You're indeed different from before.

21:17.760 --> 21:18.680
Okay, this looks good.

21:18.760 --> 21:19.720
Don't move.

21:20.240 --> 21:21.360
Okay, change your pose.

21:22.640 --> 21:24.240
I'll take a photo of you and the cake.

21:24.840 --> 21:27.360
Sangsang, where were you?

21:27.440 --> 21:28.720
We're all waiting for you. Come.

21:28.800 --> 21:31.000
- That's right.
- We're about to cut the cake.

21:31.080 --> 21:32.360
I'm so sorry.

21:32.440 --> 21:34.040
Come on, everyone. Gather around.

21:34.120 --> 21:35.360
Come here.

21:35.440 --> 21:36.360
Time to cut the cake.

21:36.440 --> 21:37.640
- Light it.
- Light the candle.

21:37.720 --> 21:39.080
- Take a picture.
- Take a picture.

21:39.160 --> 21:40.320
Wait, hold on.

21:46.920 --> 21:49.640
- Happy birthday to you
- Happy birthday to you

21:49.720 --> 21:53.040
- Happy birthday to you
- Happy birthday to you

21:53.120 --> 21:56.560
- Happy birthday to you
- Happy birthday to you

21:56.640 --> 21:59.520
- Happy birthday to you
- Happy birthday to you

22:01.080 --> 22:02.480
Make a wish!

22:02.560 --> 22:03.560
Make a wish.

22:03.640 --> 22:04.600
Okay, here I go.

22:09.400 --> 22:10.360
It's recording.

22:15.040 --> 22:16.720
- Happy birthday!
- Happy birthday!

22:16.800 --> 22:19.160
- Happy birthday!
- Happy birthday!

22:19.240 --> 22:20.880
- Cut the cake!
- All right.

22:20.960 --> 22:22.040
Let's move it over there.

22:22.120 --> 22:23.360
There's more space there.

22:24.320 --> 22:25.800
Weiwei, what time are we leaving?

22:25.880 --> 22:27.960
I reserved this room until 11 p.m. Why?

22:28.040 --> 22:29.080
Until 11 p.m.?

22:29.800 --> 22:31.760
My mom will call me.

22:32.600 --> 22:34.760
You're right. I've forgotten.

22:35.480 --> 22:36.960
Why don't you go first?

22:38.000 --> 22:39.520
How long will you guys stay?

22:39.600 --> 22:41.480
We won't stay too late.

22:41.560 --> 22:42.680
Anyway, you should go first

22:42.760 --> 22:44.160
in case your mom calls.

22:44.240 --> 22:46.160
Okay, I'll go back first.

22:46.240 --> 22:47.400
Don't stay out here too late.

22:47.480 --> 22:48.600
Okay, don't worry.

22:49.440 --> 22:50.320
I'm going back first.

22:50.400 --> 22:51.720
Remember to text us.

22:51.800 --> 22:53.440
- Stay safe.
- Be careful on your way back.

22:53.520 --> 22:54.480
Come back early.

22:54.560 --> 22:55.440
- Okay.
- Okay.

22:56.040 --> 22:57.160
- Okay, bye.
- Take care.

22:58.480 --> 22:59.880
Bring the leftover cake back for me.

23:00.360 --> 23:01.840
- Just go.
- A big slice.

23:02.320 --> 23:03.840
Remember to text us when you get back.

23:04.400 --> 23:05.240
Be careful.

23:14.320 --> 23:15.640
I'm a grown-up now.

23:15.720 --> 23:17.080
I'm no longer a kid.

23:17.160 --> 23:18.240
How old can you be?

23:18.920 --> 23:19.960
You're still a kid.

23:21.480 --> 23:22.760
That old thing.

23:26.000 --> 23:26.920
Do you mean me?

23:33.520 --> 23:34.440
I suppose so.

23:36.160 --> 23:38.600
I'm the only "old thing"

23:38.680 --> 23:40.080
that you've met tonight.

23:43.360 --> 23:44.840
I wasn't talking about you.

23:45.400 --> 23:46.640
Then who were you referring to?

23:47.800 --> 23:50.040
I was just mumbling.

23:50.520 --> 23:52.200
So tell me.

23:52.280 --> 23:53.880
Who crossed you and made you say that?

23:54.360 --> 23:55.360
I would like to know too.

23:58.480 --> 23:59.960
Jiaxu, the thing is…

24:01.840 --> 24:03.480
You don't have to be nosy.

24:04.880 --> 24:05.760
Wait.

24:08.360 --> 24:09.520
Didn't you say

24:09.600 --> 24:11.120
that you're leaving with your friends?

24:16.000 --> 24:17.120
Let's go.

24:17.200 --> 24:19.360
This old thing
will see you back to campus.

24:52.800 --> 24:53.680
Are you still cold?

24:56.600 --> 24:57.520
No.

25:13.440 --> 25:14.360
Jiaxu.

25:15.160 --> 25:16.440
Where do you live?

25:18.240 --> 25:19.400
Wenting Garden.

25:19.480 --> 25:20.600
It's near the city library.

25:22.280 --> 25:24.160
That's in the opposite direction

25:24.240 --> 25:25.400
of the campus.

25:26.000 --> 25:27.560
You will have to take a big detour.

25:28.440 --> 25:29.640
Actually,

25:30.720 --> 25:32.200
I could've gone to the metro station.

25:32.840 --> 25:33.720
Then…

25:40.120 --> 25:41.200
Young lady,

25:41.960 --> 25:44.720
I just wanted to settle a score with you

25:45.320 --> 25:46.560
while driving you back.

25:53.680 --> 25:54.560
Actually…

25:55.200 --> 25:58.600
Actually, that term

25:59.720 --> 26:01.000
is considered civilized

26:02.280 --> 26:03.600
in young people's vocabulary.

26:04.680 --> 26:05.800
I think

26:07.080 --> 26:08.960
it's not considered offensive, right?

26:09.480 --> 26:10.920
How much beer did you have tonight?

26:12.800 --> 26:13.960
One bottle.

26:17.560 --> 26:19.200
Be more careful when you go out.

26:20.200 --> 26:21.680
When you're out with strangers,

26:21.760 --> 26:23.240
it's best if you don't drink alcohol.

26:28.600 --> 26:30.360
They're not entirely strangers.

26:30.960 --> 26:33.240
We're all students
but in different departments.

26:33.920 --> 26:35.960
Besides, my roommates were there.

26:36.760 --> 26:37.840
I know.

26:37.920 --> 26:39.400
I was just reminding you.

26:59.840 --> 27:00.760
Why don't we

27:01.440 --> 27:02.440
talk for a bit?

27:05.880 --> 27:07.160
Why do I get the feeling

27:07.240 --> 27:09.400
that you have something against me, kiddo?

27:20.520 --> 27:22.080
I don't like it when you call me that.

27:27.600 --> 27:28.600
Kiddo?

27:32.600 --> 27:35.080
I am indeed five years older than you.

27:35.800 --> 27:37.240
And after you're married,

27:38.400 --> 27:40.760
your parents will still see you as a kid.

27:40.840 --> 27:42.440
So do you want to be my dad?

27:48.480 --> 27:49.360
That's not it.

27:52.600 --> 27:54.320
I mean,

27:54.400 --> 27:56.800
I'm already a grown-up, so…

27:59.120 --> 28:00.280
If you keep calling me that,

28:00.360 --> 28:01.680
I'll feel very uncomfortable.

28:05.120 --> 28:06.040
Okay.

28:06.880 --> 28:07.880
I get it.

28:30.000 --> 28:30.880
Jiaxu.

28:31.600 --> 28:33.240
What do you do now?

28:34.440 --> 28:36.480
Sang Yan said you're a programmer.

28:38.840 --> 28:40.840
Yes, I'm a game developer.

28:41.800 --> 28:42.880
A game developer?

28:44.800 --> 28:47.040
One of my roommates is a hardcore gamer.

28:47.560 --> 28:48.560
What is your game called?

28:48.640 --> 28:49.920
I can ask her about it.

28:50.600 --> 28:51.560
A Dream of Jianghu.

28:55.280 --> 28:56.520
By the way,

28:57.240 --> 28:58.320
I just remembered something.

29:00.560 --> 29:02.080
Did you choose Yihe University

29:02.160 --> 29:03.800
because of your old online friend?

29:06.320 --> 29:07.480
Am I right?

29:07.560 --> 29:08.520
No.

29:09.880 --> 29:10.840
No?

29:12.360 --> 29:13.400
It's not because of that.

29:14.600 --> 29:16.160
Yihe University's Digital Media program

29:16.240 --> 29:17.760
is the best in the country.

29:18.600 --> 29:20.720
And my scores were good enough,

29:20.800 --> 29:22.360
so of course I came to Yihe University.

29:26.320 --> 29:27.720
When I called your brother before,

29:28.240 --> 29:30.920
he seemed quite angry
about you coming to Yihe University.

29:31.440 --> 29:33.400
I thought it was because
of that old online friend.

29:35.280 --> 29:36.200
No, it wasn't.

29:36.960 --> 29:37.800
I…

29:39.000 --> 29:40.400
I haven't contacted him

29:41.240 --> 29:42.400
for a long time.

29:44.920 --> 29:45.960
I'm glad to hear that.

29:56.000 --> 29:58.360
My brother was angry

29:59.200 --> 30:01.280
because I didn't tell him

30:01.360 --> 30:02.280
when I applied.

30:03.200 --> 30:04.600
But I did tell my parents

30:05.080 --> 30:07.040
and they supported me in coming here.

30:07.600 --> 30:09.760
I didn't know what kept him busy.

30:09.840 --> 30:11.200
He didn't ask me anyway.

30:11.680 --> 30:13.040
So I didn't tell him.

30:13.120 --> 30:14.600
I thought he didn't care.

30:14.680 --> 30:16.240
But after I finished applying,

30:16.960 --> 30:17.960
he criticized me

30:18.920 --> 30:20.200
and argued with me.

30:20.280 --> 30:21.800
So of course, I argued back.

30:31.600 --> 30:32.600
Besides…

30:36.200 --> 30:37.800
Besides, I'm an adult now.

30:38.600 --> 30:40.880
I know what I'm doing.

30:45.520 --> 30:46.400
Yes,

30:47.600 --> 30:48.840
Sang Zhi is all grown up now.

30:53.920 --> 30:56.920
But you still see me as a kid.

31:24.080 --> 31:26.320
You came all the way here by yourself

31:26.400 --> 31:27.280
to attend university.

31:28.120 --> 31:29.720
Come to me if you run into any problems.

31:30.640 --> 31:31.600
Got it?

31:38.160 --> 31:40.680
I was just joking with you earlier.

31:41.360 --> 31:43.400
I know it's normal for people your age

31:43.480 --> 31:45.280
to have your own activities.

31:46.000 --> 31:47.720
I truly don't think
you have no conscience.

31:51.360 --> 31:54.360
But you did call me an old thing.

31:55.000 --> 31:56.520
How is that not considered offensive?

31:58.520 --> 32:00.960
A young lady should speak more politely.

32:03.360 --> 32:05.760
Sorry, I won't say that again.

32:07.080 --> 32:08.760
It's good that you know you're wrong.

32:10.400 --> 32:11.680
When you have free time,

32:12.440 --> 32:13.960
you can come to have a meal with me.

32:28.560 --> 32:29.520
Is it here?

32:32.680 --> 32:33.960
Make some honey water to drink

32:34.040 --> 32:35.800
to avoid waking up with a headache.

32:39.760 --> 32:41.000
Thank you, Jiaxu.

32:44.720 --> 32:45.560
By the way,

32:46.520 --> 32:47.800
I'm alone over here.

32:48.480 --> 32:49.760
So when I heard your brother say

32:49.840 --> 32:51.520
that you were coming here for university,

32:52.760 --> 32:53.680
I was really happy.

33:05.000 --> 33:06.120
Okay, go inside.

33:10.840 --> 33:11.840
I'll head inside then.

33:14.200 --> 33:15.080
See you, Jiaxu.

33:16.280 --> 33:17.120
Good night.

33:19.000 --> 33:19.960
Good night.

34:53.239 --> 34:54.280
By the way,

34:55.320 --> 34:56.800
I'm alone over here.

34:57.440 --> 34:58.920
So when I heard your brother say

34:59.000 --> 35:00.760
that you were coming here for university,

35:02.000 --> 35:03.080
I was really happy.

35:11.600 --> 35:13.560
Why would he be alone here?

35:15.680 --> 35:17.400
Isn't his home in Yihe?

35:20.560 --> 35:21.640
Besides,

35:22.520 --> 35:23.960
what about his girlfriend?

35:33.280 --> 35:34.240
JIAXU

35:34.320 --> 35:36.400
If you're ever out so late,

35:36.480 --> 35:38.080
find someone to accompany you back.

35:50.240 --> 35:52.880
SANG ZHI

35:52.960 --> 35:53.960
Okay.

35:59.320 --> 36:00.600
JIAXU

36:00.680 --> 36:03.440
Sang Zhi, check your phone and see

36:03.520 --> 36:05.040
how many messages I've sent you.

36:05.120 --> 36:06.240
You didn't reply even once.

36:06.320 --> 36:08.320
HAPPY NEW YEAR,
I SENT YOUR PARENTS GIFTS

36:08.400 --> 36:10.480
YOU GET ONE TOO,
BUT DON'T TELL SANG YAN

36:25.400 --> 36:26.400
Don't you find Chen Qiang

36:26.480 --> 36:28.400
from the Sports Department a bit weird?

36:28.480 --> 36:29.520
He giggles when he sees me.

36:31.040 --> 36:32.920
Jiang Ming is in that department too.

36:33.480 --> 36:34.600
He's a cheerful and nice guy.

36:34.680 --> 36:36.080
Do you find him weird?

36:36.160 --> 36:37.440
Well, he's not weird.

36:37.520 --> 36:38.640
But Jiang Ming

36:38.720 --> 36:41.600
already likes someone else.

36:42.920 --> 36:45.160
- Is that so?
- Yes.

36:46.320 --> 36:47.800
Really?

36:47.880 --> 36:48.920
I don't know.

36:49.480 --> 36:50.640
I know.

36:50.720 --> 36:52.360
I didn't drink a lot.

36:52.440 --> 36:55.000
Sang Yan, can you stop yelling at me?

37:05.520 --> 37:06.600
What's so funny?

37:07.960 --> 37:10.200
Sangsang, after you left last night,

37:10.280 --> 37:12.480
Jiang Ming kept asking
if you would be safe.

37:12.560 --> 37:14.120
He's quite a nice person.

37:14.640 --> 37:16.800
Has he contacted you?

37:18.880 --> 37:20.560
I haven't checked my messages yet.

37:24.080 --> 37:25.320
JIANG MING

37:26.040 --> 37:27.440
If you're ever out so late,

37:27.520 --> 37:28.800
I can accompany you back.

37:32.680 --> 37:33.560
JIAXU

37:34.680 --> 37:36.800
If you're ever out so late,

37:36.880 --> 37:38.240
find someone to accompany you back.

37:41.840 --> 37:42.880
What did he text you?

37:44.040 --> 37:45.160
Show me.

37:47.600 --> 37:48.800
He didn't say anything.

37:48.880 --> 37:50.400
Is there something that you can't share

37:50.480 --> 37:52.720
with the girls of Dorm 202?

37:56.840 --> 37:58.480
Well, there is actually something.

38:00.480 --> 38:01.840
But it's not about me.

38:03.600 --> 38:04.840
It's my friend.

38:10.200 --> 38:11.280
Sure, a friend.

38:13.240 --> 38:15.200
My friend liked her brother's friend

38:15.840 --> 38:17.320
when she was young.

38:18.800 --> 38:20.880
Her brother's friend later started dating.

38:22.080 --> 38:23.160
Then she gave up on him.

38:25.680 --> 38:27.680
But they ran into each other recently.

38:28.720 --> 38:30.520
So she doesn't know what to do.

38:30.600 --> 38:32.040
Her brother's friend?

38:32.640 --> 38:33.600
How old is he?

38:34.160 --> 38:36.240
He graduated
from university two years ago.

38:36.320 --> 38:37.800
That would mean

38:37.880 --> 38:39.760
he's about 24 to 25--

38:39.840 --> 38:40.800
He's 24.

38:41.520 --> 38:42.640
What's his job?

38:43.120 --> 38:44.160
My brother said

38:44.240 --> 38:46.160
he's a programmer who develops games.

38:46.240 --> 38:47.280
Game development?

38:48.200 --> 38:49.600
I'm an expert in that.

38:49.680 --> 38:50.560
That's right!

38:51.520 --> 38:52.600
Yu Xin.

38:52.680 --> 38:55.040
Have you heard of a game
called A Dream of Jianghu?

38:55.920 --> 38:58.160
A Dream of Jianghu
is this year's most popular game!

38:59.360 --> 39:00.360
And I'm playing it now.

39:01.440 --> 39:02.680
- Is it this?
- You're not a gamer.

39:02.760 --> 39:04.280
I need to recommend it to you.

39:04.360 --> 39:06.360
This game can be considered

39:06.440 --> 39:07.840
the hottest mobile game of the year.

39:07.920 --> 39:10.520
Whether it's the characters,
scenes, or plot design,

39:10.600 --> 39:12.080
you can say they're all top-notch.

39:12.160 --> 39:13.040
Do you see that?

39:14.480 --> 39:15.400
Did he develop it?

39:18.600 --> 39:20.160
That means he is impressive.

39:20.240 --> 39:22.600
Wait a minute. This isn't the point.

39:24.000 --> 39:25.080
The point is,

39:25.160 --> 39:27.120
does he have a girlfriend right now?

39:27.200 --> 39:28.280
That's right.

39:28.360 --> 39:29.240
Does he?

39:32.680 --> 39:33.800
I don't think so.

39:34.400 --> 39:35.720
You don't think so?

39:37.960 --> 39:40.680
So does your friend still like him?

39:42.920 --> 39:43.880
I don't think so.

39:45.280 --> 39:47.040
You don't think so?

39:48.040 --> 39:48.920
Then it's simple.

39:49.000 --> 39:49.960
If yes, go for it.

39:50.040 --> 39:51.600
If not, treat him as an ordinary friend

39:51.680 --> 39:52.720
and chat once in a while.

39:52.800 --> 39:54.040
What's the fuss?

39:54.960 --> 39:57.280
What is your friend worrying about?

40:00.280 --> 40:01.520
She's worried

40:05.240 --> 40:06.400
that this guy

40:07.520 --> 40:09.680
only sees her as a little girl.

40:11.560 --> 40:13.080
So how old

40:13.160 --> 40:14.720
was your friend

40:14.800 --> 40:16.000
when she had a crush on him?

40:17.800 --> 40:18.800
She was in high school.

40:22.080 --> 40:23.120
That's normal.

40:23.200 --> 40:24.440
You were underage at the time.

40:24.520 --> 40:25.840
If he liked you back then,

40:25.920 --> 40:27.120
he's the one with a problem.

40:30.480 --> 40:31.400
Don't interrupt.

40:33.960 --> 40:34.880
Sangsang,

40:35.360 --> 40:37.840
describe this guy to us.

40:43.240 --> 40:44.120
He's handsome.

40:44.200 --> 40:45.240
He's handsome.

40:46.760 --> 40:47.760
He had good grades.

40:51.160 --> 40:53.000
He's very interesting to talk to.

40:53.640 --> 40:54.480
He's…

40:56.480 --> 40:57.360
What?

40:58.840 --> 41:00.160
Very charismatic.

41:01.680 --> 41:03.840
He's handsome and charismatic.

41:05.280 --> 41:06.920
Then how did you two meet?

41:07.840 --> 41:09.080
He's my brother's best friend.

41:09.160 --> 41:10.640
He often came over to our house.

41:11.200 --> 41:12.600
Based on your description,

41:12.680 --> 41:13.920
he definitely has a girlfriend.

41:14.000 --> 41:15.680
It has to be so.

41:15.760 --> 41:16.680
Case closed.

41:16.760 --> 41:18.080
You don't even know him.

41:19.160 --> 41:20.520
Don't go yet. Let's talk some more.

41:21.160 --> 41:22.120
Wangwang, come on.

41:22.200 --> 41:23.280
Time to study.

41:26.920 --> 41:28.160
You guys are such mood spoilers.

41:29.120 --> 41:30.280
Forget it.

41:31.960 --> 41:33.520
I'll go and focus on my great endeavors.

41:35.120 --> 41:36.360
Don't come back too late.

41:36.440 --> 41:37.280
Okay.

41:38.080 --> 41:38.920
Be careful.

41:39.000 --> 41:40.360
- Bye.
- Stay safe.

41:40.440 --> 41:41.640
Bye.

42:18.600 --> 42:19.520
Welcome.

42:20.520 --> 42:22.200
Excuse me. Where is the honey?

42:22.280 --> 42:23.960
Sir, it's in the last aisle.

42:24.040 --> 42:25.160
Okay, thank you.

42:31.320 --> 42:34.080
HONEY

42:48.120 --> 42:49.520
- Thank you.
- Have a good night.
